TITLE: Performing Authentication with Descope SDK in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Example of using the Descope SDK to perform email OTP (One-Time Password) authentication, including sending the OTP and verifying it.
SOURCE: https://github.com/descope/descope-js/blob/main/packages/sdks/web-js-sdk/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const userIdentifier = 'identifier';
let res = await sdk.otp.signIn.email(userIdentifier);
if (!res.ok) {
  throw Error('Failed to sign in');
}

// Get the one time code from email and verify it
const codeFromEmail = '1234';
res = await sdk.otp.verify.email(userIdentifier, codeFromEmail);
if (!res.ok) {
  throw Error('Failed to sign in');
}

// Get session token
const sessionToken = sdk.getSessionToken();
```

