TITLE: Advanced OIDC Logout with Redirect
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of OIDC logout with custom post-logout redirect functionality. Demonstrates how to specify a custom redirect URL after logout.
SOURCE: https://github.com/descope/descope-js/blob/main/packages/sdks/react-sdk/README.md#2025-04-22_snippet_23

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const MyComponent = () => {
  const sdk = useDescope();

  return (
    // ...
    <button
      onClick={() => {
        sdk.oidc.logout({
          // by default, the logout will redirect the user to the current URL
          // if you want to redirect the user to a different URL, you can specify it here
          post_logout_redirect_uri: window.location.origin + '/after-logout',
        });
      }}
    >
      Logout
    </button>
  );
};
```

